  <descriptions>
      <description descriptionType="Other">This file contains the data used the community weighted mean trait analyses, with the exception of climate data which was obtained from DAYMET (Thornton et al. 2012). The &#8220;Site_Plot&#8221; column lists the site and plot identifier where the data were collected. &#8220;Date&#8221; gives the date that the trait measurements were collected. &#8220;Elevation&#8221; is the height (cm) of the center of the plot above the nearest stream. &#8220;Bulk Density&#8221; is the plot soil bulk density (g/cm3). &#8220;Days Since Burn&#8221; is the number of days since the last fire. &#8220;Shannon Index&#8221; gives the Shannon Diversity Index, H. The remaining columns give the community weighted mean SLA (g/cm3) and LDMC (%) based on the landscape level species trait averages and the plot level species values.</description>
